          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Protecting Our Military Installations from Recurrent Floods Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Defense to disclose whether any proposed major or minor military construction project requiring congressional notification or approval will be sited within or partially within a 100-year floodplain, according to the most recent available Federal Emergency Management Agency (FEMA) flood hazard data.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-04-26T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
        </item>
